{"expireTime":9007200849252696000,"key":"transformer-rehype-ast-84b515e6ca2b83f7769acf2a54930668-gatsby-rehype-inline-images-","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"ghost-themes"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ghost themes"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ghost comes with a default theme called Casper, which is designed to be a clean, readable publication layout and can be easily adapted for most purposes."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"If you need something a little more customised, it's entirely possible to build on top of existing open source themes, or to build your own from scratch. Rather than giving you a few basic settings which act as a poor proxy for code, we just let you write code."}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"marketplace"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Marketplace"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"There are a huge range of both free and premium pre-built themes which you can download from the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://ghost.org/marketplace/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ghost Theme Marketplace"}]},{"type":"text","value":":"}]},{"type":"element","tagName":"figure","properties":{"className":["kg-card","kg-image-card","kg-card-hascaption","fluid-image"],"style":["flex: 1.5822784810126582 1 0"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img-sharp-inline","properties":{"src":"https://static.ghost.org/v3.0.0/images/theme-marketplace.png","className":"kg-image","alt":"Ghost theme marketplace screenshot","fluidImg":"{\"base64\":\"data:image/png;base64,\",\"aspectRatio\":1.5822784810126582,\"src\":\"/static/628432c4ada93347af90ff1cd9b5cdd1/e8950/theme-marketplace.png\",\"srcSet\":\"/static/628432c4ada93347af90ff1cd9b5cdd1/0b533/theme-marketplace.png 500w,\\n/static/62